Debug Sidecar Container

.NET Debugging (Volume-based via diagnostic socket):
  dotnet-counters ps               - List .NET processes via diagnostic socket
  monitor-dotnet [app]             - Live performance monitoring  
  dump-dotnet [app]                - Create memory dump
  trace-dotnet [app] [secs]        - Execution tracing
  tmp-files                        - List diagnostic files in /tmp

.NET Debugging (Process namespace sharing):
  dotnet-procs                     - Show .NET processes directly
  monitor-dotnet [app]             - Live performance monitoring
  dump-dotnet [app]                - Create memory dump  
  trace-dotnet [app] [secs]        - Execution tracing

Network Monitoring:
  netmon [app]                     - All network counters
  httpmon [app]                    - HTTP client monitoring

Core Commands:
  debug-sidecar [host] [port]      - Full pod debug info
  debug-network [host] [port]      - Network connectivity tests
  loadtest-quick [url]             - Quick load test

Tools: tcpdump, nmap, mtr, netstat, ss, lsof, curl, micro
Aliases: listen, ports, conns, myip, netprocs

Examples:
  debug-sidecar api-service 8080
  test-port my-service 80
  dotnet-counters ps
